SELECT 
    'PostGoodsReceipt' || '::' || "GoodsReceipt"."ID"         AS "ID",
    "GoodsReceipt"."ID"                                       AS "MaterialMovement",
    "GoodsReceipt"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID"                  AS "PurchaseDocumentLine",
    "GoodsReceipt"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID"                  AS "PurchaseOrderLine",
    "GoodsReceipt"."ID"                                       AS "GoodsReceipt",
    "GoodsReceipt"."MaterialTransactionType"                  AS "MaterialTransactionType",
    "GoodsReceipt"."CreationTime"                             AS "Time",
    "GoodsReceipt"."CreatedBy_ID"                             AS "ExecutedBy",
    NULL                                                      AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_custom_GoodsReceipt" AS "GoodsReceipt"
WHERE "GoodsReceipt"."MaterialTransactionType" IN (
    'GoodsReceipt',
    'ReturnDeliveryToVendorReversal',
    'GoodsReceiptReversal'
)
    AND "GoodsReceipt"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
